@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_otmkth(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp + 0.39)) / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.47) / (tmp + 0.37 + v2 + 0.54)))
    v1 = (0.56 + (wp.sin(v2 + 0.44) + wp.cos(v2 + 0.57)))
    v1 = wp.cos((wp.cos(v1 + 0.87) - wp.abs(v2 + 0.94)))
    v2 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.13 + v1 + 0.52)) / (tmp - v0))
    data[tid] = v0
